name: Attack Pattern Delta
Lore: 'Snowspeeder attack plan devised by Commander Skywalker and Rebel tactician Beryl Chifonage. Single-file formation protects the squadron as the leader draws fire.',
Text: 'If a battle was just initiated at a site, identify your lead T-47 there. For remainder of this turn, all other T-47s at same site are power +1, are immune to attrition and cannot be targeted by weapons.',
